Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.02,0:00:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Encounters are mysterious!\NBut cases are even more so!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.35,0:00:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad I'm with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.52,0:00:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's case is a suspicious car!\NBe careful on the road!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.82,0:00:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He sees the\Nsingle truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.49,0:00:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and looks like a kid\Nbut has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.74,0:00:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.04,0:01:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Great Detective League Pursuit Case."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.14,0:02:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayumi-{\i1}chan{\i0}! Mitsuhiko!\NGenta! Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.77,0:02:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.60,0:02:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can count on us!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.02,0:02:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do this thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.32,0:02:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.45,0:02:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.75,0:02:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.96,0:02:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me down! Let me down from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.42,0:02:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Junior Detective League...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.21,0:02:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is victorious!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.63,0:02:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll take on any case!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.80,0:02:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll investigate any case!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.14,0:02:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And solve any case!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.43,0:02:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now.... you're bragging\Na little too much...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.18,0:02:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can count on the\NJunior Detective League!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.02,0:02:54.90,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Four Schoolchildren Catch Jewel Thief
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.29,0:03:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the food!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.50,0:03:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, you guys ate a ton!\NDon't any of you know what constraint is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.50,0:03:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go treat the kiddos to\Na meal or something, Mori-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.34,0:03:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.72,0:03:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bah. There goes all my\Nspending money for this month.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.14,0:03:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're amazing! He was\Nwanted for fifty different robberies!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.10,0:03:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun {\i0}found him! He seemed\Nsuspicious in the jewelry shop!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.86,0:03:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was just sheer luck, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.45,0:03:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we're gonna get even more clients!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.57,0:03:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! We should get our own office!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.59,0:03:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! A car's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.01,0:04:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayumi-{\i1}chan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.09,0:04:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.97,0:04:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Shinjuku 33, NA 33-96!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.26,0:04:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A hit-and-run!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.14,0:04:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran! You stay here! I'm going to\Nget the police and an ambulance!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.73,0:04:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look after her, Ran-{\i1}neechan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.57,0:04:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say a word, Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.28,0:04:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't leave this entirely to the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.15,0:04:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Hold on tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.75,0:04:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It turned!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.92,0:04:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna lose it if we don't speed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.00,0:04:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.72,0:04:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's the car!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.26,0:04:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought we lost it! Lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.69,0:05:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's stopped again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.19,0:05:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must have engine trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.16,0:05:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.24,0:05:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It stops at every turn...\NAlmost as if it's waiting for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.12,0:05:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There it goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.33,0:05:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What're you\Ndoing, Conan?! Go faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.56,0:05:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see the car...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.73,0:05:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did it finally lose us?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.44,0:05:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.40,0:05:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.11,0:05:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.28,0:05:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Is it hidden in here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.82,0:05:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, there's no place for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.41,0:05:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, it looks like this factory is closed today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.41,0:05:54.95,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Ishikura Industries
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.53,0:05:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's check around back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.50,0:06:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a bad road!\NThere's no pavement here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.80,0:06:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are stairs this way.\NWhich means...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.34,0:06:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.80,0:06:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a cigarette shop!\NLet's ask there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.31,0:06:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady! Did a red car\Njust pass by here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.27,0:06:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure. A couple\Ncars did pass by, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.82,0:06:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a two-door!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.15,0:06:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And a sports car!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.95,0:06:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know anything about cars...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.79,0:06:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.87,0:06:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's you! How're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.79,0:06:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, we've been\Nhere three minutes now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.46,0:06:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The person is\Nlong gone by now...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.38,0:06:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.55,0:06:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.18,0:06:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A red car! That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.39,0:06:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Its engine stalled again!\NWe're lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.72,0:07:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! It's different from before!\NIt wasn't there earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.73,0:07:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did it back up or something?!\NWhat for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.94,0:07:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We got it this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.82,0:07:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.21,0:07:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! We got it! Just a little more!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.05,0:07:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oww...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.63,0:07:32.59,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Beika Local Police Station
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.05,0:07:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.80,0:07:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a police station...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.93,0:07:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Officer, please arrest me.\NI committed a hit-and-run.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.06,0:07:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-He's turning himself in?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.11,0:07:50.15,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Beika Central Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.15,0:07:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He tried to run away after he hit you,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.36,0:07:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he decided to turn\Nhimself in after the guilt got to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.91,0:07:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez! How anti-climatic!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.91,0:08:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted the Junior Detective\NLeague to use more of its might!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.87,0:08:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.13,0:08:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.63,0:08:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, how is Ayumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.21,0:08:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She only got some scratches, thankfully.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.97,0:08:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They said she doesn't\Nneed to be hospitalized.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.43,0:08:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you can go home today!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.85,0:08:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great news!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.64,0:08:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it isn't. I lost the Detective\NLeague badge Conan-{\i1}kun {\i0}gave me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.86,0:08:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dropped it when you were hit?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.52,0:08:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The policeman said they didn't see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.65,0:08:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry! I can have\Nthe Doc make another one!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.66,0:08:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?! I'm so happy!\NThat's why I like you, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.50,0:08:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not fair, Conan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.33,0:08:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Buying her love with objects...\NYou coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.12,0:08:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.75,0:08:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you kids! Come with\Nme to the factory on 4th Street!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.51,0:08:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The inspector is waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.43,0:08:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The factory on 4th Street?\NThat's the place we passed by earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.89,0:09:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.85,0:09:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone died there.\NIt was apparently a murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.44,0:09:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen! You kids stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.91,0:09:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.91,0:09:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you came!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.91,0:09:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting right to the point,\Nhere's the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.58,0:09:27.79,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,President of Ishikura Industries, Ishikura Hisashi (50)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.20,0:09:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The victim was the president of this factory,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.54,0:09:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lshikura Hisashi-{\i1}san{\i0}, age 50.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.38,0:09:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This was a robbery.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.25,0:09:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we're investigating\Nit as a robbery murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.76,0:09:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The factory is closed today,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.30,0:09:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but Ishikura-{\i1}san {\i0}was apparently\Nhere alone, checking the products.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.27,0:09:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are tape marks on\Nhis mouth and wrist.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.81,0:09:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning he was strangled.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.40,0:09:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why bother\Nremoving the tape? The killer--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.19,0:09:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oww! Oww!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.82,0:09:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit scampering around the scene!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.74,0:10:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.66,0:10:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The back door is diagonal\Nfrom the cigarette lady's shop...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.75,0:10:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have to wait\Nfor the autopsy for details,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.96,0:10:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he died approximately an hour ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.88,0:10:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the same time we passed by here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.26,0:10:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No question about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.76,0:10:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought so!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.14,0:10:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see anyone suspicious then?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.10,0:10:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.81,0:10:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were focused on\Nfollowing the hit-and-run man...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.10,0:10:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! That's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.44,0:10:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See?! The guy in\Nthe back, near the middle!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.86,0:10:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! He's the one who hit Ayumi-{\i1}chan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.95,0:10:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.24,0:10:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.24,0:10:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're certain of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.70,0:10:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet he did this murder, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.25,0:10:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right! It's just coincidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.29,0:10:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Obviously!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.54,0:10:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who'd commit a robbery murder\Nwhile running from a hit-and-run?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.13,0:10:58.59,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Beika Police Department
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.92,0:11:05.56,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Former Ishikura Ind., Employee Shishido Kenichi (35)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.13,0:11:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The children started chasing me,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.76,0:11:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and my car stalled on the curve \Na little ways behind the factory.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.93,0:11:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never stopped the car behind\Nthe factory, nor did I murder anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.61,0:11:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just coincidence...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.77,0:11:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He used to work at that factory,\Nand was let go due to his misconduct.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.82,0:11:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector! You don't think...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.24,0:11:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He really did do it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.74,0:11:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He couldn't have, Genta-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.20,0:11:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.29,0:11:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were in front of the\Nfactory when it happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.83,0:11:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.58,0:11:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He could've used the back door\Nwhile he was out of the kids' sight!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.17,0:11:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but we spoke with the cigarette\Nshop lady behind the factory.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.14,0:11:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No cars stopped near here.\NNot behind the factory or on the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.69,0:11:55.94,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Location of car\NIshikura Industries
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.69,0:11:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her shop is right across from the factory's back entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.94,0:11:58.19,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Cigarette shop\NConan and friends
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.94,0:11:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her testimony can be trusted.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.19,0:12:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which would mean it\Nreally was just coincidence...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.99,0:12:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! There's another\Nside to these two incidents!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.62,0:12:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something big that we haven't noticed yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.42,0:12:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there still something else, Conan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.13,0:12:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's go visit\NAyumi-{\i1}chan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.34,0:12:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys go on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.34,0:12:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! The Junior Detective League\Nmust always work as a team!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.14,0:12:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I need juice first. I'm thirsty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.56,0:12:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's some juice over there!\NBy the cigarette shop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.07,0:12:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Wataru did?\NHe was such a studious boy, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.16,0:12:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.91,0:12:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.75,0:12:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the factory incident happened,\Ndid anyone call you by mistake?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.79,0:13:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, now that you mention it,\Nthere had been two wrong numbers...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.30,0:13:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I thought!\NAs I recall, that alleyway had--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.76,0:13:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, lady! Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.81,0:13:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on, Conan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.39,0:13:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Genta! Lift me up on your shoulders!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.52,0:13:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lift you up?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.73,0:13:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there something in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.03,0:13:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.45,0:13:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just as I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.62,0:13:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.62,0:13:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aha! That's where it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.96,0:13:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say what?! Shishido Kenichi,\Nthe hit-and-run guy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.93,0:13:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Got it, Mori-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.01,0:13:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Now for the old guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.72,0:13:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mori-{\i1}kun{\i0}? This is Megure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.31,0:14:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you hurry down\Nto the factory on 4th Street?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.73,0:14:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.49,0:14:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you, Inspector?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.82,0:14:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been expecting you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.16,0:14:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, you! What are you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.41,0:14:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector Megure will be here shortly!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.83,0:14:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait here until then!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.34,0:14:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you can be considerate!\NDon't mind if I do...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.47,0:14:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could've\Nhad at least one sip first...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.72,0:14:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just like Conan said...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.85,0:14:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He became Sleeping Kogoro\Nthe instant he entered the crime scene!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.94,0:14:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't even notice we just\Nfilled an empty can with water!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.53,0:14:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Conan! Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.53,0:14:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do next?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.37,0:14:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan told me everything.\NI'll handle things from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.37,0:14:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be serious, old guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.79,0:15:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I've made sure\Nyou'll be in the spotlight, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.54,0:15:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.92,0:15:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.92,0:15:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.88,0:15:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought him, Mori-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.30,0:15:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.68,0:15:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shishido-{\i1}san{\i0} can answer that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.22,0:15:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.85,0:15:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, you hit a little girl and drove off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.40,0:15:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You then continued to drive,\Nwith those children in pursuit,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.32,0:15:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and came by here...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.19,0:15:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...by this factory owned by Ishikura-{\i1}san{\i0},\Nwhom you know and hate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.33,0:15:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Again, what are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.58,0:15:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? So you want me to say it, after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.29,0:15:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ishikura-{\i1}san{\i0}'s killer was you,\NShishido-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.13,0:15:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now! What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.80,0:15:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was deemed innocent\Nfor the murder, at the very least!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.64,0:15:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.85,0:16:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was believed that he couldn't have\Ncommitted it while fleeing,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.27,0:16:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so he was cleared of all suspicion.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.44,0:16:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! You even have\Nsomeone to vouch for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.11,0:16:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The kids who chased me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.61,0:16:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what if that was planned?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.16,0:16:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if you intended for these children,\Nthe Junior Detective League,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.95,0:16:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to act as witnesses for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.29,0:16:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?! What do you mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.08,0:16:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In short, what if Ayumi-{\i1}kun{\i0}'s\Nhit-and-run incident
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.80,0:16:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,had been meant to camouflage the murder?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.18,0:16:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You can't be serious!\NIs that possible?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.56,0:16:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to Conan, the car would\Nunnaturally stop at each turn,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.48,0:16:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so they never lost sight of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.98,0:16:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he was doing this so they could\Nfollow him, that would explain it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.32,0:16:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My car really was in bad shape!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.99,0:16:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right, Mori-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.78,0:17:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The car's spark plugs were worn\Nand its engine was in bad condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.91,0:17:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even an amateur\Ncould set that up, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.08,0:17:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then. Even if that were the case,\NI have an alibi. A perfect one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.17,0:17:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Aside from the three\Nminutes the kids had lost sight of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.47,0:17:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do anything in three minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.85,0:17:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it would've been\Nmore than enough to enter here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.19,0:17:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.52,0:17:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The cigarette lady would've\Nseen my car stopped by the back door!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.78,0:17:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You know quite a lot...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.07,0:17:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I worked here.\NIt's only natural that I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.62,0:17:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you must naturally\Nknow that shop's phone number, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.42,0:17:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what you're getting at.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.63,0:17:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You couldn't stop the car by\Nthe back door. You walked here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.43,0:18:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what about the car?\NHow did it disappear?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.18,0:18:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.18,0:18:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.39,0:18:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.35,0:18:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where were you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.98,0:18:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.48,0:18:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show the inspector to the warehouse\Nyou lifted me up to look into!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.11,0:18:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To that warehouse?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.08,0:18:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-This car!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.66,0:18:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same as the hit-and-run car!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.66,0:18:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The number matches exactly, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.09,0:18:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shishido-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.59,0:18:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does a car exactly like\Nthe hit-and run car exist here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.05,0:18:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.60,0:18:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He probably modified a stolen car.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.64,0:18:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You worked at a sheet metal\Nand painting factory, Shishido-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.44,0:18:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would've been simple for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.27,0:19:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, you knocked Ishikura-{\i1}san\N{\i0}out with a sedative or something,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.11,0:19:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then tied him up with\Ntape and left him there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.24,0:19:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You then took the modified\Ncar and committed the hit-and-run.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.91,0:19:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You stopped the car occasionally\Nso the children could follow you,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.13,0:19:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,eventually leading them to the factory,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.01,0:19:23.97,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Factory Office\NCigarette Shop
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.01,0:19:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,after which you hid the car in the warehouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.47,0:19:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, you called the cigarette\Nlady on your cell phone,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.43,0:19:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,passed by while her\Nback was to the road,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.65,0:19:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and entered the office\Nthrough the back door.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.61,0:19:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You quickly murdered Ishikura-{\i1}san{\i0},\Nremoved the tape,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.86,0:19:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and made it look like a robbery murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.24,0:19:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The safe was probably\Nput in disarray in advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.79,0:19:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When leaving the office,\Nyou called the cigarette shop lady again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.42,0:19:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You then hurried to the\Nother hidden car, took it out,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.42,0:20:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and waited for the children at the turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.47,0:20:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, this one was your real\Ncar with your real license plate,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.77,0:20:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that you had tinkered with\Nin advance to be in bad shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.35,0:20:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.35,0:20:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How shocking!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.27,0:20:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard enough! My car was\Ntaken in after the hit-and-run!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.53,0:20:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What proof do you have otherwise?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.20,0:20:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Detective Takagi. Was there any\Nmud on the car taken into custody?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.20,0:20:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mud?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.16,0:20:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it was as clean as a new car.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.75,0:20:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are mud puddles next to the factory.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.38,0:20:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If a car passed through there,\Nmud would splatter onto its body.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.76,0:20:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you! Is there\Nany mud on that car?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.64,0:20:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Yes!\NThere is, near the bottom!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.23,0:20:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does that matter?!\NThe mud came off my car while driving!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.40,0:21:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Detective! If you're claiming that's\Nthe hit-and-run car, then prove it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.28,0:21:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.91,0:21:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.91,0:21:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mitsuhiko! Call\NAyumi-{\i1}chan {\i0}with your badge!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.95,0:21:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With my badge? But she lost hers!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.21,0:21:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just call her!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.75,0:21:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.67,0:21:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello? Ayumi-{\i1}chan{\i0}? Do you read me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.47,0:21:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Respond if you do. This is\NMitsuhiko. How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.30,0:21:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll come visit you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.10,0:21:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector! I found this badge on the car!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.85,0:21:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.94,0:21:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's--!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.02,0:21:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Ayumi's badge!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.69,0:21:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It fell out of her pocket and got\Nstuck to it during the hit-and-run!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.78,0:21:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You intended to use us for your alibi,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.62,0:21:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it seems we wound\Nup proving your guilt instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.00,0:22:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No! T-This can't be happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.47,0:23:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, Ayumi-{\i1}chan{\i0}! I found your badge!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.89,0:23:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.59,0:23:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.25,0:23:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not fair...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.68,0:23:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Conan! Where did she kiss you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.66,0:23:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us kiss you there!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.65,0:24:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? It's unlocked...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.28,0:24:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a careless household...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.20,0:24:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A blackout?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.69,0:24:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a pinprick on her back!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.27,0:24:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next Conan--
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.75,0:24:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Cooking Classroom\NMurder Case (Part 1)."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.66,0:24:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's hint:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.97,0:24:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.46,0:24:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode we attend a cooking class.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.67,0:24:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now add some pepper to the dish.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.61,0:24:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
